title: (x) Fort Worth Star-Telegram logo - custom logo by Jim Parkinson {Marc O}
content:
Looking for the font used for the Star-Telegram part (not the com).  
Any help would be appreciated! Thanks!

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20101129184119im_/http:/typophile.com/files/site_logo_340x60_3931.gif)
author: letsgobuffs

comments.content:
Custom logo by the mighty Jim Parkinson:

[http://typedesign.com/logos/startele.html](http://web.archive.org/web/20101129184119/http:/typedesign.com/logos/startele.html "http://typedesign.com/logos/startele.html")
It's a more casual, but you might like his [Pueblo](http://web.archive.org/web/20101129184119/http:/www.fontshop.com/showfont.cfm?fid=C.107056.0.0).
